OL,7,Fairs on BBC TV. It's held at the BBC
OL,8,FTelevision Centre in London. Denmark
OL,9,Fwins the contest with the song
OL,10,FDansevise, performed by Grethe and
OL,11,FJC8rgen Ingmann.
