OL,5,
OL,6,CG2020FThe main UK TV channels air an
OL,7,Faddress by Prime Minister Boris Johnson
OL,8,Fon the Covid-19 crisis. It gained an
OL,9,Faudience of 27.1m (BBC/ITV/Channel
OL,10,F4/Channel 5/Sky News/BBC News Channel),
OL,11,Fmaking it the ninth-most-watched TV
OL,12,Fprogramme in UK history.
